metadata.description:
Jeff explains why he believes the transformative AI of the 21st century will not emerge from today’s brittle and data-intensive deep learning models, but rather from sensorimotor learning systems.

00:00 Introduction: The Impact of Machine Intelligence
01:01 Questioning Deep Learning's Future & the Promise of Sensorimotor Learning
02:33 Opinions on AI's Future
04:00 Deep Learning vs. Sensorimotor Learning
10:19 Neuroscience Insights and AI
20:16 Strategic Vision for Sensorimotor AI
